{"tid":2101639,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"香港INDIE音樂人真係慘...紅唔起都算..仲要比人話編曲炫技,唔重視旋律","createTime":"2020-07-10T03:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T11:52:12.000Z","uid":55511,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"70feccac0d40d54b295136a8f1cfd7623f276ce0","tid":2101639,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"香港INDIE音樂人紅唔起原因 ：編曲過份炫技，唔重視旋律<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2101394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2101394</a><br />\n首先我係好明顯從呢個post得到靈感 意在簡單分析評鑑下indie音樂人既歌  睇下係咪好似入邊樓主講既咁<br />\n 入邊樓主第一個point 話好似雞蛋蒸肉餅，MY LITTLE AIRPORT,佢地偏向外國小眾曲風，追求冷門和弦，編曲用左好多進階技巧<br />\n於是我走入去求其搵幾首聽下 雞蛋蒸肉餅我第一次聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4yB4SMKnl7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4yB4SMKnl7A&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=f83b3af3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4yB4SMKnl7A</a><br />\n呢首: 固定音型[C# D# C# D# C# G#,A...]老實講有啲煩<br />\nchord 37跟住個固定音型咁loop 成首一次都冇走出過c# minor scale(印象中連chord都冇)<br />\n就同我印象中既追求冷門和弦相去甚遠<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=58QS5POhkug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D58QS5POhkug&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=d3206ba7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=58QS5POhkug</a><br />\n<br />\n唯一聽到有少少心思係後面有兩個人聲做副旋律 男女聲一低一高夾住主旋律 算係成首我聽落黎唯一覺得好既地方<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U7ebN0GHVDo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU7ebN0GHVDo&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=843c5531\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U7ebN0GHVDo</a><br />\n呢首同樣啲音樂材料好簡單 chord幾乎一兩個咁loop 旋律幾乎都係分解和弦 歌詞:榴槤乜乜乜...<br />\n開頭成分鐘都停留係E大三和弦 我第一次聽即刻閂左 第二次聽到中間先知佢想做乜 <br />\n佢靠堆疊電結既聲部 想製造一種絢爛既效果 雖然係我心目中硬係唔夠完美 唔知係條bass啲級進太煩 定係佢缺乏一個穩定和弦既內聲部(長線條,尤其最中間唱緊榴槤乜乜乜果段) 定係吉他唔夠多 雖然係咁講 我都係睇到佢係呢首編曲上既心思 你話係咪炫技 我又覺得未去到果個level(睇你同邊個比..)<br />\n<br />\n跟住到MY LITTLE AIRPORT 一段時間之前我覺得佢地好垃圾 連唱歌都走音<br />\n然後我再聽番 覺得佢地好神 首先佢果種走音  係完美解決左廣東話9音係唔fit in係12音階入邊造成唱起上黎有種好硬既感覺<br />\n都唔知佢地到底係咪特登(有時傾向呢隻<img src=\"https://drumlessonsbeginners.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/hi-hat-closed.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrumlessonsbeginners.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F04%2Fhi-hat-closed.gif&h=b646c609&s={SIZE}\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-awnwjlFLfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-awnwjlFLfw&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=7f88178f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-awnwjlFLfw</a><br />\n入邊呢首 vocal幾乎每個音個frequency一出完都會飄 然後旋律就算直出都有機會直接++--(hz)<br />\n多數- 因為+既話你對走音既觀感會比較強 除左ti音 雖然係咁 首歌出黎個效果好好 好舒服<br />\n敢膽玩frequency呢樣野都算令佢走上技術最尖端(其中一樣) 起碼淨係以呢個方面呢計可以話佢旋律係jacob collier級 (唔計佢用咩音高材料既話) <br />\n 拎呢首黎對比下 會唔會覺得vocal條女 對音高把控同mla有啲似<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LgR5nA4uSSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLgR5nA4uSSc&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=fa78968b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LgR5nA4uSSc</a> <br />\n當然mla既和弦詞彙完全都係少 又係成首都冇離開過Bmajor scale咁濟(用左次c#o)<br />\n<br />\n結論:以上兩隊預期話係輕視旋律追求冷門和弦 我覺得係完全相反 旋律唔覺有大問題 mla仲好正  而佢地須要注重更多係提升和聲方面素養  留意和聲色彩 用多啲和弦 轉調離調  等等 <br />\n而唔係長期用幾個loop晒成首 成首同一個調咁 因為會好悶  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea564f2586a8aa0f3643cc5e8ba141d301fcbd6a","tid":2101639,"uid":306738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n留名"},{"pid":"1a19611ca62c346d554d717ab115ff44bf676277","tid":2101639,"uid":104122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"睇完佢個po我都有就harmony同arrangement分析咗少少嗰個po樓主俾嘅example<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qcnuyJX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qcnuyJX</a> 有興趣可以討論下 屌細力D thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢係慣咗standard ballad/rock嘅編曲方法<br />\n要variation轉少少樂器對佢已夠了<br />\n成個arrangement format轉太多了<br />\n所以佢覺得會炫技<br />\n<br />\n至於佢話和弦冷門真係唔知佢想講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa42a67f432e2800b2a61866ab00ec2e03f7c98","tid":2101639,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"不過我完全冇諗過MLA係玩緊microtonality &amp; tones<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我就算睇完樓主analysis都唔係好明點聽<br />\n我自己覺得jacob collier好聽係因為佢有做preparation<br />\n同每個microtone都有原因<br />\n<br />\n相反MLA D歌跳上跳落又冇preparation<br />\n仲要跳落microtones<br />\n真係聽唔入耳<br />\n或者係我都俾12tet同western melodic rules困住咗個思維吧<br />\n真係聽嚟聽去都覺得只係一條冇加任何注意、先詞後曲格硬嚟嘅melody<br />\n<br />\n如果樓主可以detail少少哋analyse可以講少少嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08232b84a8295642bad26e86e251b7907761860d","tid":2101639,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a19611ca62c346d554d717ab115ff44bf676277","tid":2101639,"uid":104122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"睇完佢個po我都有就harmony同arrangement分析咗少少嗰個po樓主俾嘅example<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qcnuyJX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qcnuyJX</a> 有興趣可以討論下 屌細力D thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢係慣咗standard ballad/rock嘅編曲方法<br />\n要variation轉少少樂器對佢已夠了<br />\n成個arrangement format轉太多了<br />\n所以佢覺得會炫技<br />\n<br />\n至於佢話和弦冷門真係唔知佢想講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"我諗佢係想講9 11 13 extends 或者 生得似polychord 個樣奇奇怪怪果啲chord<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7374033dd69bb80390d6c70cf3326dbfb46a4d96","tid":2101639,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fa42a67f432e2800b2a61866ab00ec2e03f7c98","tid":2101639,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"不過我完全冇諗過MLA係玩緊microtonality &amp; tones<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我就算睇完樓主analysis都唔係好明點聽<br />\n我自己覺得jacob collier好聽係因為佢有做preparation<br />\n同每個microtone都有原因<br />\n<br />\n相反MLA D歌跳上跳落又冇preparation<br />\n仲要跳落microtones<br />\n真係聽唔入耳<br />\n或者係我都俾12tet同western melodic rules困住咗個思維吧<br />\n真係聽嚟聽去都覺得只係一條冇加任何注意、先詞後曲格硬嚟嘅melody<br />\n<br />\n如果樓主可以detail少少哋analyse可以講少少嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"preparation即係指咩preparation 我諗mla都係跟feel去唱的 佢係有果個sense一早就肯改下啲chord"},{"pid":"c57c8647170ac2ba3ced130a3910990e21bba68b","tid":2101639,"uid":104122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08232b84a8295642bad26e86e251b7907761860d","tid":2101639,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a19611ca62c346d554d717ab115ff44bf676277","tid":2101639,"uid":104122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"睇完佢個po我都有就harmony同arrangement分析咗少少嗰個po樓主俾嘅example<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/qcnuyJX\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/qcnuyJX</a> 有興趣可以討論下 屌細力D thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im